title: Ford GT - Incredible 360 degree Onboard lap of Silverstone! #360Video #VR #FordWEC #6hSilverstone
description:
Get inside the the awesome Ford GT racing car  on a 360 degree virtual reality lap of Silverstone - shot during the 2016 WEC Silverstone Race weekend.  Looking weird? For 360 best effect, try watching this in the YouTube app on your smartphone!

You may not all be able to join us for the race at Silverstone but this will get you pretty close to the real thing! Comments below... and please like and share!
